I love roblox! my favorite games are Adopt Me, Welcome to Bloxburg, Doors, Piggy, Royale High, Brookhaven, Mega Easy Obby 100 Stages, Training Simulator, Superhero Tycoon, Epic Minigames, Pet Simulator. I have so much robux! One time I took my mom's credit card and spent 200 dollars on robux. I even have a roblox girlfriend. :)

Some of my favorite youtubers include LankyBox, DenisDaily, Tofuu, GamingWithKev, Flamingo, KreekCraft, and more! I hope to be like them some day and make roblox videos!
